&lt;li&gt;You are gritty, resilient and ready to roll up your sleeves and make things happen.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’re looking to utilize your multilingual skills and work with a diverse group of driven talent.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You&#39;re looking to develop a strong business acumen and work across different industries.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
